<h1>API Documentation</h1>

<h2>Creating a new tinyThom.as</h2>

<p>If you'd like to generate a tinyThom.as through the REST API, you'll just need to POST an XML or JSON request to <strong>http://tinythom.as/api/link</strong>.</p>

<p>To view the example XML requests and responses, <a href="http://gist.github.com/229106">view these examples</a>.</p>

